                                    "title": "Lazy Initialization",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Delay the creation of an object until it is needed, improving startup performance and resource usage."
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Example implementation across language variants."
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "code",
                                            "path": "design_patterns/lazy_initialization"
