                                    "id": "proxy",
                                    "title": "Proxy",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Proxy is sometimes categorized as a structural pattern, sometimes as a behavioral pattern. It's included here for simplicity. If we wanted to be more precise, we could split it into two patterns: Proxy (structural) and Virtual Proxy (behavioral). For now, we'll keep it as a single pattern"
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Provide a surrogate or placeholder to control access to another object."
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Example implementation across language variants."
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "code",
                                            "path": "design_patterns/proxy"
                                        }
