                                    "title": "Data Mapper",
                                    "content": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Separate the in-memory objects from the database, allowing for a clean domain model and flexible data access."
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "text",
                                            "text": "Example implementation across language variants."
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "code",
                                            "path": "design_patterns/data_mapper"
